---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-16 px-4 bg-background text-text">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Image Collage with larger middle image -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-7 gap-2 w-full">
        <div class="col-span-2 h-40 overflow-hidden mt-20">
          <img src="/images/one.jpg" alt="Beach sunset with people" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-3 h-80 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/two.jpg" alt="Group on beach with palm trees" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-2 h-40 overflow-hidden mt-20">
          <img src="/images/three.jpg" alt="Family on beach" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Taglines -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <p class="italic text-lg mb-1">Intentional & natural</p>
      <p class="italic text-lg mb-1">Connected to the land & each other</p>
      <p class="italic text-lg mb-6">Purposefully slow & absolutely unforgettable</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Description Text -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="mb-8">
        Choosing to elope was an easy decision for you. (Giant, extravagant weddings? So not you.)
        <br>But we're here to make this even easier. We combine planning and photography to create one
        <br>all-inclusive elopement tailored to you.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Divider with Text -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
        <div class="w-1/6 border-t border-border"></div>
        <p class="px-4 text-lg text-heading italic">
          We can't wait to welcome you to Maui and plan 
          <br>your totally custom, all-inclusive elopement.
        </p>
        <div class="w-1/6 border-t border-border"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <button class="bg-button hover:bg-hover text-buttontext py-4 px-8 transition-colors duration-300 w-44 text-center">
        <p class="uppercase tracking-wide text-xs mb-1">THIS IS GONNA BE YOUR</p>
        <p class="italic">best. day. ever.</p>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>